OL,5,Ctourism hotspots
OL,6, Hotel worker Jon Phillips has given up
OL,7, trying to rent a home near his job in
OL,8, Cornwall and is now living on his boat.
OL,10,F"My landlord said: 'Look Jon, you're
OL,11,Fpaying me #800 a month for this one
OL,12,Fbedroom apartment, and I've just found
OL,13,Fout that I can be charging people on
OL,14,Fholiday #1,200 a week.'"
